  <brief_title>PleuraSeal Pivotal Study (US)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Multicenter Randomized Clinical Study to Evaluate the PleuraSeal Sealant System as an Adjunct to Standard Closure Techniques for Control of Visceral Pleural Air Leaks Following Elective Pulmonary Resection Via Open Thoracotomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
